If you see a creator who’s work is TOP NOTCH! This is how they began too - low quality videos with a low quality camera, no sense of angles, no sense of backgrounds, color grading, aesthetics - NOTHING! But what they all had in common ? - Dedication to CREATE despite the fact they had NO idea how all of this works! If you want to create, and have NO idea how it’s going to work out for you - Listen to me! Pick up your camera, SHOOT that video and POST it! You’ll eventually learn like we all did. And trust me - you won’t regret it! ❤️
